Title: Provide caller's IP in web.log for errors arising from agent updater requests
Class: feature
Compatible: compat
Component: agents
Date: 1629712185
Edition: cee
Knowledge: undoc
Level: 1
Version: 2.1.0b1

This is an addition to Werk #10435, where the caller's hostname, if provided in the
request, was added to the error information.
Now, to overcome situations with a missing or incorrectly specified hostname,
the caller's IP is logged additionally.
